{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_018X1mdKBHmzrRFmL4TNQELA","type":"tool_result","content":"   420â†’## Container Isolation Model\n   421â†’\n   422â†’- **Files in**: `docker cp` copies the project into `/workspace/`. No bind mounts. Override files from `.cloche/overrides/` are applied on top. `.git/` is included.\n   423â†’- **Files out**: On completion, the daemon extracts results via `docker cp` into a git worktree and commits to a `cloche/<run-id>` branch.\n   424â†’- **Auth files**: `~/.claude/` and `~/.claude.json` are copied into each container at `/home/agent/` for Claude Code session reuse. Copied (not bind-mounted) so each container gets its own isolated copy.\n   425â†’- **Network**: Containers have network access (needed for API calls).\n   426â†’- **Cleanup**: Containers are removed after successful runs unless `--keep-container` is set. Failed runs always keep their container.\n   427â†’\n   428â†’Your project directory is never modified by the container.\n   429â†’"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8ea6a4db-317b-4116-946b-dfa5f420f957","uuid":"92ddc0ff-a9c5-4342-b816-c3d3f4126bd6","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/docs/USAGE.md","content":"## Container Isolation Model\n\n- **Files in**: `docker cp` copies the project into `/workspace/`. No bind mounts. Override files from `.cloche/overrides/` are applied on top. `.git/` is included.\n- **Files out**: On completion, the daemon extracts results via `docker cp` into a git worktree and commits to a `cloche/<run-id>` branch.\n- **Auth files**: `~/.claude/` and `~/.claude.json` are copied into each container at `/home/agent/` for Claude Code session reuse. Copied (not bind-mounted) so each container gets its own isolated copy.\n- **Network**: Containers have network access (needed for API calls).\n- **Cleanup**: Containers are removed after successful runs unless `--keep-container` is set. Failed runs always keep their container.\n\nYour project directory is never modified by the container.\n","numLines":10,"startLine":420,"totalLines":639}}}
